divs: sighting detailswhile walking my dog on the hike and bike trail next to my apt., i watched a long, backwards-flying triangle (pointed end at back) with one dimly-lit, non-blinking, white light at each tip traveling from south of the u.s.-mexico border heading in a northerly direction. at first, i only saw one light and thought maybe it was a satellite. then i saw the other two lights at fixed points from the first light outlining its shape. it almost appeared as though i could make out some kind of hazy-looking, transparent body\structure to the object. i could not tell the altitude of the object nor the speed. it appeared to be a very large object traveling at a high rate of speed (100s of mile\hr)at a great altitude. i did not hear any sound emanating from object. i stopped dead in my tracks while watching this object until it was out of sight having been blocked from view by a building. i had a very surreal feeling like i had discovered something that wasn't supposed to be seen.
